<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="5">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">匿名用户、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lu-xiao-teng-40" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lu-xiao-teng-40" class="zg-link" title="陆泊言">陆泊言</a></span>
